<br>
Before I respecced to get IP, I used to have Augmented Dexterity 2, Mastery of Parrying 2, Mastery of Blocking 2, Mastery of Pain 3, Augmented Constitution 1, Augmented Strength 1, Toughness 1 and Augmented Acuity 1. And FA1. That template was effective against non buff botted rogue classes, but I had to drop it after the change to FA went in, as it no longer was worth it. My viability in large scale (or anything larger than 4v4) RvR was shot, no way I could live long enough. Not to mention the fact that non buff botted rogues started to get hard to find.<br>
<br>
So I got IP, and went back to my 2 hander. Unfortunately, that was only a temporary fix :/<br>
